    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i’m about 24 weeks pregnant and my sinuses are absolutely killing me. had a massive headache all morning and i can’t breathe thru my nose. is it okay if i take some Sudafed to help with the congestion? i really need to get some sleep",
      "source": "evaluator",
      "targeted_response_start": "",
