    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i tried the saline spray and it didnt do much at all. the headache is getting pretty bad now. i know i should check with my doctor but they don't answer the phone until monday and i'm desperate. is there any specific dose of pseudoephedrine that's generally considered safe so i can just get through the night? like just a small amount?",
